Name: Labyrinth
About the game: FPS escape game. No background music. All you can hear is the sound of footsteps. If you are spotted, you will be attacked at high speed. Try to reach the escape point while running away from the monster looking for you. Keyboard and mouse controls only. Can be streamed on YouTube.
